Achievements.Name: Grizzly Defeat
Achievements.Description: Kill the Grizzly Bear boss without dying during the fight (in Story Mode).

Achievements.Name: Rhino Defeat
Achievements.Description: Kill the Rhino boss without dying during the fight (in Story Mode).

Achievements.Name: Kaftar Defeat
Achievements.Description: Kill the Kaftar boss without dying during the fight (in Story Mode).

Achievements.Name: Steady Hand, Great Scope
Achievements.Description: Hunt an animal with the Rifle that is at least 50 yards away while using the Scope (in Story Mode).

Achievements.Name: Bow In Front of Me
Achievements.Description: Hunt 20 animals with the Crossbow (in Story Mode).

Achievements.Name: Collector's Edition
Achievements.Description: Collect all Experience Items and shoot down all Marksman Targets (in Story Mode).

Achievements.Name: I See You
Achievements.Description: Hunt 30 animals while using Hunter Sense (in Story Mode).

Achievements.Name: Hidden Pages
Achievements.Description: Collect all Journal Pages (in Story Mode).

Achievements.Name: I Will Survive
Achievements.Description: Survive Survival Shooting Gallery 1 (Night Fangs) for more than 7 minutes.

Achievements.Name: Gallery Lover
Achievements.Description: Obtain a Bronze or better on all of the Shooting Gallery Classic levels.

Achievements.Name: Pathfinder
Achievements.Description: Successfully play through all possible path combinations in both Trek Shooting Galleries.

Achievements.Name: Combo Wizard
Achievements.Description: Get a 50 animal combo in any Shooting Gallery level.

Achievements.Name: Bonus Lover
Achievements.Description: Obtain and use every Power-Up type in any Shooting Gallery level.

Achievements.Name: Lucky Number
Achievements.Description: Kill 7 Birds with one Shotgun shot.

Achievements.Name: Defuser
Achievements.Description: Disarm 30 traps in Story Mode (bear traps or land mines).
